Player Faction Ranks

Rebel
1) Ensign - Rebel Uniform ~ Starting Rank for all Rebels
2) Lieutenant - Rebel Captain's Armor / DC-15S Carbine or DC-15x Sniper Rifle 
3) SpecOps Agent - Infilitrator's Armor
4) Admiral - Rebel's Body Armor
5) Commander - Service Special

Jedi
1) Initiate - Jedi Signet Ring ~ Starting Rank for all Jedi
2) Padawan - Lightsaber
3) Knight - Jedi Knight Robe
4) Master - Jedi Hood
5) Grand Master - Jedi Master Robe

Stormtrooper
1) Private - Stormtrooper Armor ~ Starting Rank for all Stormtroopers
2) Captain - Stormtrooper Captain's Armor / E-11[or B] Blaster Rifle 
3) Commando - Clone Trooper Phase II Armor
4) Officer - Imperial Officer Uniform
5) Moff - Service Special

Sith
1) Adept - Sith Signet Ring ~ Starting Rank for all Sith
2) Apprentice - Lightsaber
3) Master - Dark Jedi Knight Robe
4) Darth - Dark Jedi Hood
5) Dark Lord - Dark Jedi Master Robe

Trader
1) Trader - Trader Badge / Access ~ Starting Rank for all Traders
2) Merchant - Access to Wholesale NPC
3) Proprietor - Own Stand
4) Executive - Own Store
5) President - Store Taxes
